{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "mpesa-prod-stk-001",
		"name": "M-Pesa Production - STK Push (Buy Goods)",
		"description": "# M-Pesa Production API Collection\n\nThis collection contains endpoints for testing M-Pesa STK Push (Lipa na M-Pesa Online) in **PRODUCTION** environment.\n\n## ⚠️ IMPORTANT WARNINGS\n\n- **This uses LIVE/PRODUCTION APIs** - Real money will be charged!\n- **Use with caution** - Only test with small amounts\n- **Ensure you have valid production credentials** from Safaricom Developer Portal\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n1. **Production Credentials** (from https://developer.safaricom.co.ke/):\n   - Consumer Key\n   - Consumer Secret\n   - Short Code (Till Number)\n   - Passkey (for your Till Number)\n\n2. **Set Environment Variables** in Postman:\n   - `mpesa_consumer_key` - Your production consumer key\n   - `mpesa_consumer_secret` - Your production consumer secret\n   - `mpesa_shortcode` - Your Till Number (e.g., 9584650)\n   - `mpesa_passkey` - Your production passkey\n   - `callback_url` - Your callback URL (must be publicly accessible)\n\n## Usage Flow\n\n1. **Get Access Token** - Run this first to get an OAuth token\n2. **Initiate STK Push** - Send payment request to customer's phone\n3. **Query STK Push Status** - Check payment status (optional)\n\n## Production URLs\n\n- OAuth: `https://api.safaricom.co.ke/oauth/v1/generate`\n- STK Push: `https://api.safaricom.co.ke/mpesa/stkpush/v1/processrequest`\n- STK Query: `https://api.safaricom.co.ke/mpesa/stkpushquery/v1/query`\n\n## Transaction Type\n\nThis collection uses **CustomerBuyGoodsOnline** transaction type for Till Numbers (Buy Goods).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Get OAuth Access Token",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    if (jsonData.access_token) {",
							"        pm.environment.set(\"mpesa_access_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
							"        console.log(\"Access token saved to environment variable\");",
							"    }",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "basic",
					"basic": [
						{
							"key": "username",
							"value": "{{mpesa_consumer_key}}",
							"type": "string"
						},
						{
							"key": "password",
							"value": "{{mpesa_consumer_secret}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "https://api.safaricom.co.ke/oauth/v1/generate?grant_type=client_credentials",
					"protocol": "https",
					"host": [
						"api",
						"safaricom",
						"co",
						"ke"
					],
					"path": [
						"oauth",
						"v1",
						"generate"
					],
					"query": [
						{
							"key": "grant_type",
							"value": "client_credentials"
						}
					]
				},
				"description": "Get OAuth 2.0 access token for production M-Pesa API.\n\n**Token is valid for 1 hour (3600 seconds)**\n\n**Authentication:** Basic Auth using Consumer Key and Consumer Secret"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "2. Initiate STK Push (Buy Goods)",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Generate timestamp in format: YYYYMMDDHHmmss",
							"var now = new Date();",
							"var year = now.getFullYear();",
							"var month = String(now.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var day = String(now.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var hours = String(now.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var minutes = String(now.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var seconds = String(now.getSeconds()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var timestamp = year + month + day + hours + minutes + seconds;",
							"",
							"// Generate password: Base64(SHORTCODE + PASSKEY + TIMESTAMP)",
							"var shortcode = pm.environment.get(\"mpesa_shortcode\");",
							"var passkey = pm.environment.get(\"mpesa_passkey\");",
							"var passwordString = shortcode + passkey + timestamp;",
							"",
							"// Base64 encode (Postman uses btoa for base64 encoding)",
							"var password = btoa(passwordString);",
							"",
							"// Set environment variables",
							"pm.environment.set(\"mpesa_timestamp\", timestamp);",
							"pm.environment.set(\"mpesa_password\", password);",
							"",
							"console.log(\"Generated Timestamp: \" + timestamp);",
							"console.log(\"Password (Base64): \" + password);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    if (jsonData.CheckoutRequestID) {",
							"        pm.environment.set(\"checkout_request_id\", jsonData.CheckoutRequestID);",
							"        pm.environment.set(\"merchant_request_id\", jsonData.MerchantRequestID);",
							"        console.log(\"CheckoutRequestID saved: \" + jsonData.CheckoutRequestID);",
							"    }",
							"    ",
							"    // Check response code",
							"    if (jsonData.ResponseCode === \"0\") {",
							"        console.log(\"✅ STK Push initiated successfully!\");",
							"        console.log(\"Customer Message: \" + jsonData.CustomerMessage);",
							"    } else {",
							"        console.log(\"❌ STK Push failed: \" + jsonData.ResponseDescription);",
							"    }",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{mpesa_access_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n    \"BusinessShortCode\": \"{{mpesa_shortcode}}\",\n    \"Password\": \"{{mpesa_password}}\",\n    \"Timestamp\": \"{{mpesa_timestamp}}\",\n    \"TransactionType\": \"CustomerBuyGoodsOnline\",\n    \"Amount\": \"1\",\n    \"PartyA\": \"254712345678\",\n    \"PartyB\": \"{{mpesa_shortcode}}\",\n    \"PhoneNumber\": \"254712345678\",\n    \"CallBackURL\": \"{{callback_url}}\",\n    \"AccountReference\": \"TEST-{{$timestamp}}\",\n    \"TransactionDesc\": \"Test Payment\"\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "https://api.safaricom.co.ke/mpesa/stkpush/v1/processrequest",
					"protocol": "https",
					"host": [
						"api",
						"safaricom",
						"co",
						"ke"
					],
					"path": [
						"mpesa",
						"stkpush",
						"v1",
						"processrequest"
					]
				},
				"description": "Initiate STK Push payment request for Buy Goods (Till Number).\n\n**⚠️ This will send a payment prompt to the customer's phone!**\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `BusinessShortCode`: Your Till Number\n- `Password`: Auto-generated (Base64 encoded)\n- `Timestamp`: Auto-generated (YYYYMMDDHHmmss)\n- `TransactionType`: `CustomerBuyGoodsOnline` (for Till Number)\n- `Amount`: Amount in KES (whole number, no decimals)\n- `PartyA`: Customer phone number (254XXXXXXXXX format)\n- `PartyB`: Your Till Number\n- `PhoneNumber`: Customer phone number (254XXXXXXXXX format)\n- `CallBackURL`: Your callback URL (must be publicly accessible)\n- `AccountReference`: Unique reference for this transaction\n- `TransactionDesc`: Description of the transaction\n\n**Before running:**\n1. Update `PartyA` and `PhoneNumber` with actual test phone number\n2. Update `Amount` with test amount\n3. Ensure `callback_url` environment variable is set"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "3. Query STK Push Status",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Generate timestamp in format: YYYYMMDDHHmmss",
							"var now = new Date();",
							"var year = now.getFullYear();",
							"var month = String(now.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var day = String(now.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var hours = String(now.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var minutes = String(now.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var seconds = String(now.getSeconds()).padStart(2, '0');",
							"var timestamp = year + month + day + hours + minutes + seconds;",
							"",
							"// Generate password: Base64(SHORTCODE + PASSKEY + TIMESTAMP)",
							"var shortcode = pm.environment.get(\"mpesa_shortcode\");",
							"var passkey = pm.environment.get(\"mpesa_passkey\");",
							"var passwordString = shortcode + passkey + timestamp;",
							"var password = btoa(passwordString);",
							"",
							"// Set environment variables",
							"pm.environment.set(\"mpesa_timestamp\", timestamp);",
							"pm.environment.set(\"mpesa_password\", password);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    ",
							"    // ResultCode meanings:",
							"    // 0 = Success",
							"    // 1032 = User cancelled",
							"    // 1037 = Timeout",
							"    // 1 = Failed",
							"    ",
							"    if (jsonData.ResultCode === \"0\") {",
							"        console.log(\"✅ Payment successful!\");",
							"    } else if (jsonData.ResultCode === \"1032\") {",
							"        console.log(\"❌ User cancelled the payment\");",
							"    } else if (jsonData.ResultCode === \"1037\") {",
							"        console.log(\"⏱️ Payment timeout\");",
							"    } else {",
							"        console.log(\"❌ Payment failed: \" + jsonData.ResultDesc);",
							"    }",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{mpesa_access_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n    \"BusinessShortCode\": \"{{mpesa_shortcode}}\",\n    \"Password\": \"{{mpesa_password}}\",\n    \"Timestamp\": \"{{mpesa_timestamp}}\",\n    \"CheckoutRequestID\": \"{{checkout_request_id}}\"\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "https://api.safaricom.co.ke/mpesa/stkpushquery/v1/query",
					"protocol": "https",
					"host": [
						"api",
						"safaricom",
						"co",
						"ke"
					],
					"path": [
						"mpesa",
						"stkpushquery",
						"v1",
						"query"
					]
				},
				"description": "Query the status of an STK Push payment request.\n\n**Use this if:**\n- Callback is delayed\n- You want to check payment status manually\n- Debugging payment issues\n\n**Required:**\n- `CheckoutRequestID` from the STK Push initiation response\n\n**Result Codes:**\n- `0` = Payment successful\n- `1032` = User cancelled\n- `1037` = Timeout\n- `1` = Failed\n- Other codes = Various error conditions"
			},
			"response": []
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "mpesa_consumer_key",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_consumer_secret",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_shortcode",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_passkey",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "callback_url",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_access_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "checkout_request_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "merchant_request_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_timestamp",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "mpesa_password",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	]
}
